---
// StatsSection.astro
---

<section class="stats-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="stats-grid grid grid-3">
      <!-- Card 1: Orange Primary -->
      <div class="stat-card card-orange">
        <div class="stat-icon-wrapper">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-truck"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="stat-number">15K+</h3>
        <h4 class="stat-title">Mercadorias Entregues</h4>
        <p class="stat-desc">Transportes de grande e médio porte realizados com sucesso absoluto em rodovias e portos.</p>
        <ul class="stat-features">
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Coleta Agendada no Mesmo Dia</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Embalagem Segura Certificada</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/services" class="btn btn-white btn-stat">Conhecer Serviços</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Dark Navy -->
      <div class="stat-card card-dark">
        <div class="stat-icon-wrapper">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-face-smile"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="stat-number">20K+</h3>
        <h4 class="stat-title">Clientes Satisfeitos</h4>
        <p class="stat-desc">Parcerias corporativas de longo prazo baseadas na confiabilidade de entrega de suprimentos.</p>
        <ul class="stat-features">
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> 99.8% de Feedbacks Positivos</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Redução de 15% nos Custos</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/about" class="btn btn-primary btn-stat">Quem Somos</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: Orange Secondary -->
      <div class="stat-card card-orange">
        <div class="stat-icon-wrapper">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-users"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="stat-number">30K+</h3>
        <h4 class="stat-title">Equipe Técnica Especializada</h4>
        <p class="stat-desc">Profissionais treinados e prontos para lidar com processos aduaneiros e fretes de risco.</p>
        <ul class="stat-features">
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Engenheiros Logísticos</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Despachantes Aduaneiros 24/7</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-white btn-stat">Fale Conosco</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .stats-section {
    position: relative;
    padding: 0;
    margin-top: -80px; /* Overlaps with previous section for premium visual style */
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .stats-grid {
    gap: 1.5rem !important;
  }

  .stat-card {
    padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    transition: all var(--transition-normal);
  }

  .stat-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
  }

  .card-orange {
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .card-dark {
    background-color: var(--color-primary-light);
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .stat-icon-wrapper {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .card-orange .stat-icon-wrapper {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .card-dark .stat-icon-wrapper {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .stat-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .stat-desc {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8) !important;
  }

  .stat-features {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .stat-features li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .stat-features i {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .btn-stat {
    margin-top: auto;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .stats-section {
      margin-top: 0;
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }
  }
</style>
